{"tid":1685823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突破樽頸位］朝早開波 被動三罷","createTime":"2019-10-31T19:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T15:58:21.000Z","uid":15362,"like":81,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"98cb4890f72bb0c9a1b8084ee61f1948e6a23428","tid":1685823,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:02:49.000Z","msg":"個個咁多藉口要翻工 <br />\n我地朝早開波全港被動罷工 <br />\n醜人由我地黎做包贏<br />\n<br />\n十八區開花避埋交通問題 <br />\n<br />\n就係睇大家敢唔敢早起身一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間 早上530集合 日子待定<br />\n<br />\n手法 封路爆鐵 <span style=\"color: red;\">最近你既主要公路去封就得 市區交比住市區既手足</span><br />\n<br />\n原因 夠新夠突發班狗部署唔到 同埋有埋翻工人士cover比埋藉口香港人唔翻工 <br />\n<br />\n目的 制造被動三罷<br />\n<br />\n目標 連續三日朝早開波 達致癱瘓香港既效果<br />\n<br />\n作戰細節 堵塞主要公路 爆埋狗鐵<br />\n<br />\n緊記快閃 要有哨兵 不與狗鬥 小心狗鐵有伏狗<br />\n<br />\n服裝 黑外套內雜色衫<br />\n<br />\n裝備 以爆破裝備為主 其他裝備自己決定帶唔帶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEjkJ5xQwff1mvhcng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEjkJ5xQwff1mvhcng&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=502c648d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEjkJ5xQwff1mvhcng</a>"},{"pid":"90e4e0d925577325c650fa8bd256b59858beeaa3","tid":1685823,"uid":15362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:04:49.000Z","msg":"重新開左post好多手足反映 太快做唔切文宣 <br />\n同埋時間太早  <br />\n<br />\n大家同意呢個方法可以突破現時既樽頸請推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050e72581f01e976e2a6aa2e90ce633c72e1eacb","tid":1685823,"uid":152114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:05:14.000Z","msg":"個宣傳級數一定要好大先work<br />\n好似十月一咁"},{"pid":"f8ebdac94d9b677529cfaf450a5b67c4e19103e7","tid":1685823,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"想贏就平日既朝頭早開波 十八區開花 直接全港被動罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1683488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1683488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<b